        "description": "ORDER. It is hereby ordered that defendants' 99 motion to dismiss is GRANTED in part and DENIED in part as outlined in this order. It is further ordered that defendants' 101 request for judicial notice is GRANTED in part and DENIED in part as outlined in this order. It is further ordered that Luo's 107 motion to strike is GRANTED in part and DENIED in part. The clerk is court is kindly instructed to strike exhibit 1 (ECF No. 100 -1) to the Declaration of John B. Lawrence. It is further ordered that Lou's 114 motion for leave to file supplemental authority is DENIED. This matter is referred to the magistrate judge for a settlement conference. Local Rule 16-5. If the parties are unable to reach an agreement resolving the claim, Luo will have the option to amend his complaint within fifteen days of the failed settlement conference. Signed by Judge Cristina D. Silva on 10/7/2024. (Copies have been distributed pursuant to the NEF - ALZ) (Entered: 10/08/2024)",
